# Optional: list rule basenames (one per line) to omit from the Slack / employee-factory
# persona bundle. Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# When to add excludes:
# - Index-only files whose content is duplicated by the full rules linked from them
#   (you already exclude alex-trigger and alex-factory via --compact).
# - Large reference modules that stay in `.cursor/rules/` for Cursor IDE but blow the
#   default LLM_SYSTEM_MAX_RUNES (48k) budget for Slack. See `employee-factory` router
#   hints: hints must point at modules that remain in the bundle.
#
# Navigation map (levers point to fully inlined files):
alex-growth-levers.mdc
# Token-heavy; smaller modules cover closers; full blueprint stays in repo for IDE:
alex-ultimate-sales-blueprint.mdc
# Long reference lists; not needed for short Slack replies:
alex-facts-list-masters.mdc
alex-clear-proof.mdc
alex-hard-conversations-upfront.mdc
alex-awareness-give-ask.mdc
# Overlap with stair-step / one-channel / stress rules still in bundle:
alex-obscurity-boom.mdc
alex-mental-toughness.mdc
